ActCorporations Returns Act
SubjectCorporations Returns Regulations
PrecisCORPORATIONS RETURNS REGULATIONS in order to (1) bring the number of corporations subject to the Act back in line with the original intent of the Act by raising the reporting thresholds; (2) reflect amendments made to the Act over time; and (3) update certain forms.
